    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabattas</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half and add to one side of a baking tray</p><p>Add your <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> to the other side of the baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for 3-4 min or until everything is toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 5,
