    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once toasted, remove the tray[s] from the oven and transfer the <strong>roasted pumpkin seeds</strong> to a plate</p><p>Top the <strong>toasted ciabattas</strong> with the <strong>goats' cheese rarebit sauce</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven and cook for 6-8 min or until the rarebit sauce is lightly browned – these are your <strong>goats' cheese rarebit toasts</strong></p>",
