    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and <strong>orange rounds </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>pomegranate seeds </strong>with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>and toss – this is your <strong>pomegranate & orange salad</strong></p>",
