      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>goats' cheese rarebit toasts</strong> with the <strong>wedges</strong> and <strong>pomegranate & orange salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>thyme honey </strong>over the rarebit toasts and top the salad with the <strong>roasted pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
